<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Successful - JayLink SMS</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset styles */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #0284c7;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #0284c7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .success-alert {
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #e8f5e8;
      border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .success-alert strong {
      color: #2e7d32;
    }
    .amount-display {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .amount {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4caf50;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .amount-label {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .details-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #fafafa;
    }
    .details-table td {
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .details-table td:first-child {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #555;
      width: 40%;
    }
    .details-table td:last-child {
      color: #333;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }
    .details-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .transaction-id {
      font-family: monospace;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #4caf50;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .social {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .social a {
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #0284c7;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Jay<span style="color: #0369a1;">Link</span> SMS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Payment Successful!</h2>
      <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
      
      <div class="success-alert">
        <strong>âœ… Payment Processed Successfully!</strong><br>
        Your account has been credited instantly and is ready for use.
      </div>
      
      <div class="amount-display">
        <div class="amount">{{formatCurrency amount currencySymbol}}</div>
        <div class="amount-label">Successfully Added to Your Account</div>
      </div>
      
      <p>Here are your transaction details:</p>
      
      <table class="details-table">
        <tr>
          <td>Amount Paid:</td>
          <td class="highlight">{{formatCurrency amount currencySymbol}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Payment Method:</td>
          <td>{{paymentMethod}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Reference Number:</td>
          <td><span class="transaction-id">{{reference}}</span></td>
        </tr>
        {{#if transactionId}}
        <tr>
          <td>Transaction ID:</td>
          <td><span class="transaction-id">{{transactionId}}</span></td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
        <tr>
          <td>New Account Balance:</td>
          <td class="highlight">{{formatCurrency newBalance currencySymbol}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Transaction Date:</td>
          <td>{{formatDate timestamp}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      
      <p>Your account is now ready for use! You can start sending SMS messages, making voice calls, and using all our premium features.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{balanceUrl}}" class="button">View Account Balance</a>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> Keep your transaction reference number safe. You can use it to track this payment or for support inquiries.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing JayLink SMS. We're here to help you communicate effectively!</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The JayLink Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} JayLink SMS. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="social">
        <a href="#">Twitter</a> | <a href="#">Facebook</a> | <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
      <p>This is an automated email confirmation. Please do not reply to this message.<br>
      If you have questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>